  "Description": {
    "English": "A supersymmetric particle cluster created by divergent super-gravitational forces. A <span class=\"name name-stellar\">micro-rift</span> is created as they form, and extraction of the orb prompts a localised reality weakening. <span class=\"name name-fuel\">Sentinel forces</span> will respond to stabilize any such anomaly.<br><br>Can be sold at a <span class=\"name name-technology\">Galactic Trade Terminal</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "在发散超重力作用下形成的超对称粒子簇。它们形成时会产生一个<span class=\"name name-stellar\">微型裂缝</span>，提取球体会促生局部现实弱化。<span class=\"name name-fuel\">护卫部队</span>会做出反应来稳定这种异象。<br><br>可以在<span class=\"name name-technology\">银河交易终端</span>出售。",
    "TencentChinese": "超对称粒子簇。<br><br>这种在发散超重力作用下形成的产物极其稀有、极具价值。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "超對稱粒子群集，是發散型異端超級重力所產生。此種粒子群集生成時，亦會產生<span class=\"name name-stellar\">微裂痕</span>，將其取出即會導致當地現實弱化。<span class=\"name name-fuel\">巡警部隊</span>會立即反應，穩定化此類異常。<br><br>可在<span class=\"name name-technology\">銀河交易終端站</span>出售。"
  },
